; This has been extracted from
; https://github.com/tldr-pages/tldr/blob/master/pages/common/gh-pr-comment.md

% gh-pr-comment, common

# Comment on the pull request of the current branch
gh pr comment <__b___body_> "<LGTM>"

# Comment on a specific pull request
gh pr comment <123> <__b___body_> "<Thanks_>"

# Comment from a file
gh pr comment <123> <__F___body_file_> <path_to_file_txt>

# Open the editor to write a multi-line comment
gh pr comment <123>
